# Flutter Migration Rules

- Read the Flutter widget file first, understand intent, then write idiomatic RN
- Never do a direct line-by-line translation from Dart to TypeScript
- StatefulWidget + setState → useState hook
- Provider/Riverpod → Redux slice + useAppSelector
- Bloc/Cubit → Redux Toolkit createSlice
- FutureBuilder → RTK Query useXxxQuery hook
- StreamBuilder → Supabase Realtime + useEffect subscription
- ListView.builder → FlatList
- Column/Row → View with flexDirection
- Navigator.push → navigation.navigate with typed params
